headline: MNST Q2 Deep Dive: Global Growth, Innovation Pipeline, and Margin Expansion
summary: Energy drink company Monster Beverage (NASDAQ:MNST) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 11.1% year on year to $2.11 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.52 per share was 8.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
